    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "rebuild what? there is nothing left to rebuild. the people i worked with, the people who believed in me... i let them all down. the truth is that i'm just a failure. people like me, we don't just \"grow\" from this. we just exist in the wreckage. it doesn't feel like a lesson, it just feels like the end.",
